<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Painel - SharkBotzap</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      color: #333;
    }
    header {
      background-color: #1e40af;
      color: white;
      padding: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header img {
      height: 40px;
    }
    main {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .info {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .cards {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card {
      flex: 1 1 180px;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f9fafb, #d1d5db);
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    .qr {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .qr img {
      max-width: 100%;
      border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .btn {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s ease-in-out;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #1d4ed8;
    }
    .instructions {
      background: #f9fafb;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .instructions h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>SharkBotzap</h1>
  </header>
  <main>
    <div class="info">
      <h2>Bem-vindo, <%= user.name %></h2>
      <p>Email: <strong><%= user.email %></strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card">
        <strong>Status:</strong><br>
        <span><%= status.status %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <strong>√öltima A√ß√£o:</strong><br>
        <span><%= status.lastMessage || '-' %></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <% if (qr) { %>
      <div class="qr">
        <p>Escaneie o QR Code abaixo com o WhatsApp:</p>
        <img src="<%= qr %>" alt="QR Code WhatsApp">
      </div>
    <% } else if (status.status !== 'conectado') { %>
      <p style="text-align:center;">Nenhum QR Code dispon√≠vel. Clique no bot√£o abaixo para conectar.</p>
    <% } %>

    <% if (status.status !== 'conectado') { %>
      <form action="/dashboard/conectar" method="POST">
        <button class="btn" type="submit">Conectar WhatsApp</button>
      </form>
    <% } else { %>
      <form action="/dashboard/desconectar" method="POST">
        <button class="btn" type="submit">Desconectar WhatsApp</button>
      </form>
    <% } %>

    <form action="/dashboard/aquecedor" method="POST">
      <button class="btn" type="submit">Iniciar Aquecedor</button>
    </form>

    <div class="instructions">
      <h3>üìò Instru√ß√µes de Uso</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Clique em "Conectar WhatsApp" para gerar o QR Code.</li>
        <li>Escaneie o QR Code com seu aplicativo WhatsApp.</li>
        <li>Ap√≥s conectado, voc√™ pode iniciar o aquecimento autom√°tico.</li>
        <li>Para trocar de n√∫mero, clique em "Desconectar WhatsApp".</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
  <footer>
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SharkBotzap. Todos os direitos reservados.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
